{"tid":1996111,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"中國爆「甲殼類神秘病毒」　死亡率八成！不排除突變後傳染給人類","createTime":"2020-04-30T18:11:46.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-01T07:35:13.000Z","uid":219007,"like":6,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"ec552b6244798d63d12949e05611e548b80f809b","tid":1996111,"uid":219007,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-30T18:11:46.000Z","msg":"武漢肺炎疫情未解除，近日中國又再爆遭神秘病毒侵襲，而且更對沿海地區11省市中招，這種病毒被稱為「甲殼類神秘病毒」，在蝦、蟹之間高度傳播，發病率六成、死亡率高達八成，沒有藥物治療，日本媒體更指，這種病毒不排除與禽流感病毒，突變後傳染給人類。<br />\n<br />\n據香港《蘋果日報》報導，這種神秘病毒的消息，中國只有針對水產養殖戶的雜誌《水產前沿》有報導。文中指出，今年華南地區的蝦病問題嚴重，廣東珠三角、汕尾、饒平、福建等地，部份地區出現大批病例，發病率高達六成，多項測試均指向一種名為「蝦虹彩病毒」有關。2017年春季，廣東湛江、陽江、粵東和福建的漳浦、長樂等地發現高密度養殖的南美白對蝦出現爆發性死亡<br />\n<br />\n報導指出，這種由「虹彩病毒1」（Decapod iridescent virus 1, DIV 1）病毒引發的新型病毒，沒有太典型的病徵，多數只出現肝胰腺萎縮、顏色變淺、腳變黑、停止攝食、活力下降等，只能靠養蝦大量死亡而斷定。往年則曾在廣東、浙江、河北等地流行，而海洋研究單位則在浙江養殖的南美白對蝦，及在紅螯螯蝦中發現這種病毒。且這種新病毒沒有特效藥，只能以清潔池塘、定時清理污物、不使用鮮活飼料等才能預防。<br />\n<br />\n日本的《周刊郵報》（NEWSポストセブン）報道這次事件，指2013至2018年間，病毒令中國白蝦產量減少30萬噸，雖然這種病毒目前不會傳染給人，但也不排除如同禽流感病毒，突變後傳染給人類。（即時新聞中心／綜合報導）<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://tw.appledaily.com/international/20200430/LIO4BURT3TD4L4PUVZOKFWWSEY/?utm_campaign=twad_social_appledaily.tw&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_content=link_post\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20200430%2FLIO4BURT3TD4L4PUVZOKFWWSEY%2F%3Futm_campaign%3Dtwad_social_appledaily.tw%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_content%3Dlink_post&d=IJrjZyikD9iZithZGIL3rEPYNnpCCLo8Mp68exG%2FaA0%3D&h=38fa93f2\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20200430%2FLIO4BURT3TD4L4PUVZOKFWWSEY%2F%3Futm_campaign%3Dtwad_social_appledaily.tw%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_content%3Dlink_post&h=59e22c5e\" target=\"_blank\">https://tw.appledaily.com/international/20200430/LIO4BURT3TD4L4PUVZOKFWWSEY/?utm_campaign=twad_social_appledaily.tw&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_content=link_post</a>"},{"pid":"247516f7d0d3b5cbba47df663375d5319d281528","tid":1996111,"uid":41389,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-30T18:12:34.000Z","msg":"天滅啦"},{"pid":"24388f262dbdd924d09ca5e23a88c3c09c43bae8","tid":1996111,"uid":118322,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-30T18:13:05.000Z","msg":"一定又係美國佬搞事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"41371ecd652e4a94a2f3fb6e1f00fb2c528b4b83","tid":1996111,"uid":48286,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-30T18:15:05.000Z","msg":"班芝麻人食獨角仙<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"688dea352431dd13ed07086cba34dd5155f6fa15","tid":1996111,"uid":327462,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-30T18:17:12.000Z","msg":"新甲病毒<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a378b3dd36a407a0cc4d3b674f5598f708976ddf","tid":1996111,"uid":295563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-30T18:17:21.000Z","msg":"又少一樣食物lu"},{"pid":"030908d203af796be0290e599b2e73a8be9ebdaf","tid":1996111,"uid":2054,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-30T18:18:16.000Z","msg":"中國人永遠唔會令人失望<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4ded45d1bbff3fa0d3ab551751d3d773af5a0cc9","tid":1996111,"uid":40439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-30T18:33:04.000Z","msg":"咁撚鍾意食小龍蝦呀拿<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7a39a86bd29a779a93ae566d2cc4787b3a0a109e","tid":1996111,"uid":273218,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-30T18:42:19.000Z","msg":"可能同濫用抗生素 ，醫療污染，同濫捕物種破壞平衡呢d因素做成?反正支那係衰呢幾樣"},{"pid":"eaab46f1df1b58db400c101d81e87b3b934849f0","tid":1996111,"uid":2757,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-30T19:01:29.0